gw.api.job

Class EffectiveDateCalculator

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.job.EffectiveDateCalculator

  • public class EffectiveDateCalculator
extends java.lang.Object
    Calculates a date and time for a given job effective date, taking the IEffectiveTimePlugin's time component into consideration.
